Chapter: Codex Types

 Type representations used by the type checker and later stages.

Section: Primitive Types

  CodexType =
   | IntegerTy
   | NumberTy
   | TextTy
   | BooleanTy
   | CharTy
   | VoidTy
   | NothingTy
   | ErrorTy
   | FunTy (CodexType) (CodexType)
   | ListTy (CodexType)
   | LinkedListTy (CodexType)
   | TypeVar (Integer)
   | ForAllTy (Integer) (CodexType)
   | SumTy (Name) (List SumCtor)
   | RecordTy (Name) (List RecordField)
   | ConstructedTy (Name) (List CodexType)
   | EffectfulTy (List Name) (CodexType)

  SumCtor = record {
   name : Name,
   fields : List CodexType
  }

  RecordField = record {
   name : Name,
   type-val : CodexType
  }

